title: PetSmart 's revenue in the U.S. 2014/15 - 2019/20
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Revenue in million U.S. dollars, containing a total of 6 data points.
In general Revenue in million U.S. dollars has rose over the Year.
Revenue in million U.S. dollars is roughly constant from 2014/15 to 2017/18, and lastly slightly increasing from 2017/18 to 2019/20.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2017/18 and 2018/19.
The highest Revenue in million U.S. dollars, of value 7091.1 was reached at Year 2019/20
The lowest Revenue in million U.S. dollars, of value 4900.8 was reported at Year 2014/15
